18
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 39 =

20
00:01:39,940 --> 00:01:41,380
= Wang Gongchen, courtesy name Junkuang =

21
00:01:41,380 --> 00:01:42,100
Your Majesty,

22
00:01:43,340 --> 00:01:44,900
I was splitting hairs

23
00:01:45,300 --> 00:01:46,340
and holding extreme views.

24
00:01:46,820 --> 00:01:48,260
My demented behavior

25
00:01:48,260 --> 00:01:49,140
embarrassed Your Majesty.

26
00:01:49,380 --> 00:01:50,300
I am conscious of my dreadful crime.

27
00:01:51,140 --> 00:01:52,620
I deserve to be punished.

28
00:02:01,460 --> 00:02:02,300
Your Majesty,

29
00:02:03,580 --> 00:02:05,180
what I did might cost my life,

30
00:02:05,700 --> 00:02:07,220
but I don’t regret it.

31
00:02:08,300 --> 00:02:10,020
My extreme behavior

32
00:02:10,780 --> 00:02:12,020
annoyed Your Majesty

33
00:02:12,700 --> 00:02:14,060
and was teased by other officials.

34
00:02:16,580 --> 00:02:17,700
But it made Your Majesty

35
00:02:18,820 --> 00:02:20,980
reconsider the ruling on Teng Zongliang,

36
00:02:22,420 --> 00:02:26,860
which made any punishment worthwhile.

37
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:46,900
That is not extreme behavior.

38
00:02:48,820 --> 00:02:51,780
You are disturbing public affairs
out of personal hatred.

39
00:03:07,100 --> 00:03:09,540
I don’t want to say too much

40
00:03:09,540 --> 00:03:10,740
about what kind of punishment to Teng Zongliang

41
00:03:11,300 --> 00:03:13,300
would be fair.

42
00:03:14,580 --> 00:03:15,940
I just want to tell you

43
00:03:16,940 --> 00:03:19,260
many civil officials, who claimed themselves lofty,

44
00:03:19,780 --> 00:03:21,820
are ruined by

45
00:03:21,820 --> 00:03:23,500
angling for undeserved fame.

46
00:03:25,820 --> 00:03:27,020
Learn to conduct yourself well.

47
00:03:33,380 --> 00:03:34,420
That’s it for today.

48
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:35,260
You are dismissed.

49
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:54,260
Your Majesty.

50
00:03:59,980 --> 00:04:01,780
Fan Zhongyan and Fu Bi are about to leave
the Capital.

51
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:04,220
Redundancy reduction has been very successful,

52
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:05,420
same for official management.

53
00:04:06,340 --> 00:04:07,660
Now we should slow down or suspend

54
00:04:07,780 --> 00:04:09,700
redundancy and elimination.

55
00:04:19,300 --> 00:04:20,340
In my opinion,

56
00:04:21,220 --> 00:04:22,500
Your Majesty, you put the redundancy

57
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:24,180
as well as the corruption elimination
as the priority

58
00:04:24,820 --> 00:04:26,460
like cleaning the dirt.

59
00:04:27,460 --> 00:04:28,060
Once

60
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:29,940
a large space is cleaned out,

61
00:04:30,260 --> 00:04:31,340
you might as well manage
and operate this space first

62
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:34,100
before cleaning the remaining

63
00:04:34,820 --> 00:04:35,820
dirty places.

64
00:04:39,620 --> 00:04:41,180
I understand

65
00:04:41,180 --> 00:04:42,020
they want to have a radical cure.

66
00:04:42,660 --> 00:04:45,180
I know they are loyal to the country.

67
00:04:45,900 --> 00:04:48,700
But now the resentment has reached the highest,

68
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:50,860
