71
00:05:06,020 --> 00:05:07,020
To me,

72
00:05:07,820 --> 00:05:10,420
stressing agriculture and commerce
is to recuperate and build up strength,

73
00:05:12,140 --> 00:05:13,740
while setting up public schools
and supporting private schools

74
00:05:14,700 --> 00:05:16,500
is at the core of improving the intelligence
of people, and

75
00:05:17,660 --> 00:05:19,940
nourishing the long-lasting vigor of our nation.

76
00:05:53,140 --> 00:05:54,140
I can only remember you

77
00:05:54,660 --> 00:05:56,620
