80
00:06:05,860 --> 00:06:07,060
and border affairs.

81
00:06:07,700 --> 00:06:09,460
I don’t want to disturb you

82
00:06:09,460 --> 00:06:10,540
or distract you.

83
00:06:10,820 --> 00:06:11,700
Knowing that

84
00:06:11,700 --> 00:06:13,300
you are doing well

85
00:06:13,460 --> 00:06:14,940
from someone around you

86
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:16,220
is enough to me.

87
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:22,180
You often drive me mad,

88
00:06:23,060 --> 00:06:24,380
but never distract me

89
00:06:24,540 --> 00:06:26,420
from state affairs.

90
00:06:29,740 --> 00:06:31,100
I’m guilty

91
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:33,180
for making you angry.

92
00:06:37,300 --> 00:06:38,260
I mean

93
00:06:38,540 --> 00:06:40,100
you can come by when you are available,

94
00:06:41,020 --> 00:06:43,300
and you won’t disturb me.

95
00:06:44,460 --> 00:06:45,820
You don’t need to send someone

96
00:06:46,020 --> 00:06:47,460
to exhort people around me.

97
00:06:55,700 --> 00:06:56,420
Well?

98
00:07:03,380 --> 00:07:04,220
Your Majesty,

99
00:07:07,180 --> 00:07:08,580
I…

100
00:07:10,460 --> 00:07:12,300
So why did you wait for me at Hall of Arch

101
00:07:12,340 --> 00:07:13,980
not worrying that you would disturb me?

102
00:07:15,780 --> 00:07:16,580
Let me guess.

103
00:07:18,380 --> 00:07:19,420
Is it because

104
00:07:19,420 --> 00:07:21,580
the marriage between Taotao and Zongshi is settled

105
00:07:21,580 --> 00:07:22,660
and Xinhe couldn’t sit still?

106
00:07:22,860 --> 00:07:24,020
Which boy did you two

107
00:07:24,340 --> 00:07:25,940
choose for Huirou?

108
00:07:27,660 --> 00:07:28,460
Your Majesty,

109
00:07:31,020 --> 00:07:34,380
Zuixinglai might get pestilence.

110
00:07:36,380 --> 00:07:38,020
Huirou hasn’t shown any symptom yet,

111
00:07:38,220 --> 00:07:39,300
but physicians said

112
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:40,620
maybe

113
00:07:42,620 --> 00:07:45,700
