117
00:07:58,460 --> 00:07:59,900
They were stung by ticks

118
00:07:59,900 --> 00:08:01,540
while hanging out in the garden.

119
00:08:06,100 --> 00:08:07,500
Do you remember

120
00:08:08,220 --> 00:08:11,220
my uncle got this disease too

121
00:08:11,460 --> 00:08:14,420
when he was in the army?

122
00:08:15,020 --> 00:08:16,900
At that time, half of the army was infected.

123
00:08:19,140 --> 00:08:20,020
That year...

124
00:08:22,740 --> 00:08:23,860
In 1027 A.D.,

125
00:08:25,980 --> 00:08:26,940
half of 5000 people

126
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:30,460
in the army,

127
00:08:31,140 --> 00:08:32,980
were infected, more than a thousand of them died.

128
00:08:32,980 --> 00:08:33,660
It is said that

129
00:08:35,340 --> 00:08:37,260
tick is carrier of the disease.

130
00:08:38,860 --> 00:08:39,740
Physicians said

131
00:08:40,740 --> 00:08:42,380
if they are having a fever after being stung,

132
00:08:43,140 --> 00:08:44,340
maybe the situation won’t be

133
00:08:44,340 --> 00:08:45,900
as terrible as that time.

134
00:08:46,620 --> 00:08:47,420
Maybe

135
00:08:48,460 --> 00:08:50,380
