136
00:08:50,620 --> 00:08:51,900
just like ordinary flu.

137
00:08:53,620 --> 00:08:54,420
But

138
00:08:55,660 --> 00:08:58,900
the infective can directly infect

139
00:08:58,940 --> 00:09:00,620
people around them,

140
00:09:00,940 --> 00:09:02,540
so I commanded...

141
00:09:02,700 --> 00:09:03,940
Why didn’t you tell me earlier?

142
00:09:09,420 --> 00:09:10,660
At the Hall of Arch,

143
00:09:11,300 --> 00:09:12,180
I thought

144
00:09:12,500 --> 00:09:14,100
it’s not an appropriate time

145
00:09:15,260 --> 00:09:16,500
to let officials know

146
00:09:16,860 --> 00:09:18,340
Zuixinglai might be infected.

147
00:09:19,140 --> 00:09:20,500
Maybe it’s just a false alarm.

148
00:09:21,460 --> 00:09:22,500
But if people know,

149
00:09:22,780 --> 00:09:24,100
it might cause chaos.

150
00:09:26,540 --> 00:09:27,300
Your Majesty,

151
00:09:30,340 --> 00:09:32,540
I came here to tell you that

152
00:09:33,020 --> 00:09:34,340
you can’t go to the Pavilion of Phoenix.

153
00:09:35,620 --> 00:09:37,100
If Huirou and Zuixinglai

154
00:09:37,220 --> 00:09:38,500
were infected,

155
00:09:38,780 --> 00:09:39,540
Your Majesty!

156
00:09:45,260 --> 00:09:49,300
Your Majesty, after I report it to you,

157
00:09:50,700 --> 00:09:51,940
I shall move into the Pavilion of Phoenix

158
00:09:52,940 --> 00:09:54,620
to take care of Huirou and Zuixinglai

159
00:09:54,620 --> 00:09:55,860
with Madam Miao.

160
00:09:57,500 --> 00:09:58,980
But Your Majesty,
you’re the ruler of the whole country,

161
00:10:00,740 --> 00:10:02,100
you can’t take any risk.

162
00:10:05,060 --> 00:10:07,180
Huirou and Zuixinglai

163
00:10:08,220 --> 00:10:09,980
are my flesh and blood, my everything!

164
00:10:10,340 --> 00:10:11,140
Your Majesty...

165
00:10:11,140 --> 00:10:11,780
Shut up!

166
00:10:12,660 --> 00:10:13,620
I don’t want you to tell me

167
00:10:13,620 --> 00:10:14,740
I’m the Emperor of the country.

168
00:10:15,380 --> 00:10:16,340
I am the Emperor,

169
00:10:16,780 --> 00:10:17,620
but I’m also

170
00:10:17,620 --> 00:10:18,900
their father.

171
00:10:20,300 --> 00:10:21,700
I want to see my children.

172
00:10:22,380 --> 00:10:23,100
Move away!

173
00:10:27,860 --> 00:10:29,580
I swear with my life

174
00:10:30,180 --> 00:10:32,220
I’ll do everything I can to take care of them.

175
00:10:32,220 --> 00:10:33,300
I’ll feed them medicine in person.

176
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:35,260
If anything happens to them,

177
00:10:36,540 --> 00:10:39,380
I shall take any punishment from Your Majesty.

178
00:10:54,060 --> 00:10:56,660
= The Empress Cao holds hatred and grievance
in heart, breaks rules repeatedly =

179
00:10:58,420 --> 00:10:59,140
You...

180
00:11:01,620 --> 00:11:04,660
I, Cao Danshu, didn’t give birth to a single child

181
00:11:05,820 --> 00:11:06,900
after being the Empress for years.

182
00:11:08,180 --> 00:11:10,340
If I didn’t take good care
of the prince and princess,

183
00:11:10,820 --> 00:11:13,220
I deserve to be deposed for failing in my duty.

184
00:11:14,740 --> 00:11:16,220
I’ve written the decree

185
00:11:16,220 --> 00:11:17,340
and Your Majesty should keep it.

186
00:11:18,020 --> 00:11:19,180
If the princess and the prince

187
00:11:19,180 --> 00:11:20,460
can recover

188
00:11:20,460 --> 00:11:21,420
safe and sound,

189
00:11:21,420 --> 00:11:22,500
then burn it.

190
00:11:23,740 --> 00:11:27,100
Otherwise, do what it says.

191
00:11:28,740 --> 00:11:30,140
Why do you do this?

192
00:11:30,580 --> 00:11:32,060
I always trust you.

193
00:11:32,100 --> 00:11:32,740
I just…

194
00:11:32,740 --> 00:11:34,620
Your Majesty are just worried and anxious

195
00:11:35,020 --> 00:11:36,220
about your children.

196
00:11:38,540 --> 00:11:39,540
But I

197
00:11:39,540 --> 00:11:42,300
can’t suffer pain from the disease
for Huirou or Zuixinglai.

198
00:11:42,940 --> 00:11:44,260
There’s nothing else I can do.

199
00:11:46,580 --> 00:11:47,860
If you remove me,

200
00:11:49,060 --> 00:11:50,780
you can choose another empress immediately.

201
00:11:50,780 --> 00:11:51,740
But Your Majesty,

202
00:11:53,940 --> 00:11:55,340
if you and Zuixinglai are sick

203
00:11:55,340 --> 00:11:56,620
at the same time,

204
00:11:57,740 --> 00:11:58,740
when Xixia just gained peace,

205
00:11:58,940 --> 00:12:00,780
Fan Zhongyan and Fu Bi are about to leave
the Capital,

206
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:03,980
rumors are wide spread about the rebellion
of Shi Jie and Fu Bi.

207
00:12:04,580 --> 00:12:05,500
At this critical moment,

208
00:12:07,940 --> 00:12:11,020
who can stabilize the court for you?

209
00:12:35,380 --> 00:12:37,340
= Fu Mansion =

210
00:12:37,340 --> 00:12:38,100
Yanguo.

211
00:12:39,340 --> 00:12:40,100
Mr. Fan.

212
00:12:43,820 --> 00:12:45,820
Even without any good wine,

213
00:12:46,060 --> 00:12:47,860
I must come to see you off.

214
00:12:50,460 --> 00:12:52,260
The prince suddenly became restless

215
00:12:52,740 --> 00:12:55,100
at 2:00 a.m. last night.

216
00:12:55,460 --> 00:12:57,140
This morning, he had gum bleeding

217
00:12:57,620 --> 00:13:00,460
and a few purple rashes on his back.

218
00:13:01,060 --> 00:13:03,940
I believe it’s not caused by summer heat,

219
00:13:04,540 --> 00:13:07,700
but the pestilence spread by ticks.

220
00:13:10,620 --> 00:13:11,740
Prince’s disease

221
00:13:12,100 --> 00:13:13,580
was found in time.

222
00:13:15,180 --> 00:13:17,300
The medicine for reducing fever he had yesterday

223
00:13:17,500 --> 00:13:19,420
does not go against the treatment of this disease?

224
00:13:19,980 --> 00:13:20,700
Yes, yes.

225
00:13:21,180 --> 00:13:23,900
But the prince is young,

226
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:26,220
and the attack is so abrupt.

227
00:13:26,540 --> 00:13:29,420
He’s still not out of danger.

228
00:13:30,820 --> 00:13:31,900
As for the princess,

229
00:13:32,140 --> 00:13:33,700
she doesn’t have any symptom for now,

230
00:13:34,060 --> 00:13:35,060
but you’re still not sure

231
00:13:35,060 --> 00:13:36,460
if she’ll be sick later?

232
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:39,220
Still not sure.

233
00:13:39,540 --> 00:13:41,180
It takes at least 3 or 5 days.

234
00:13:41,780 --> 00:13:43,500
The maids who are serving the prince

235
00:13:43,780 --> 00:13:45,420
should be very careful.

236
00:13:46,060 --> 00:13:47,260
Their food

237
00:13:47,340 --> 00:13:49,380
needs to be separated from others’.

238
00:13:50,060 --> 00:13:51,580
Just do whatever that needs to be done.

239
00:13:52,140 --> 00:13:53,860
If you need maids and eunuchs,

240
00:13:54,140 --> 00:13:54,940
just tell me

241
00:13:55,220 --> 00:13:56,500
a number.

242
00:13:56,940 --> 00:13:58,420
I’ll tell Ren Shouzhong to arrange it immediately.

243
00:14:00,540 --> 00:14:02,380
You’ll leave the Capital in a few days.

244
00:14:02,900 --> 00:14:03,900
There are many proposals and decrees

245
00:14:03,900 --> 00:14:05,780
to hand over in the Cabinet.

246
00:14:06,020 --> 00:14:06,980
With so many things to do,

247
00:14:07,500 --> 00:14:08,420
