248
00:14:08,420 --> 00:14:09,340
just to see me off?

249
00:14:10,220 --> 00:14:12,140
Besides, the so-called clique

250
00:14:12,540 --> 00:14:13,860
is like a knife

251
00:14:13,860 --> 00:14:14,780
hanging above our heads.

252
00:14:18,300 --> 00:14:20,580
Zhigui, Zimei and Yongshu still

253
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:22,900
serve with important positions in the Capital.

254
00:14:23,060 --> 00:14:24,900
So naturally they shouldn’t come to see you
off to avoid trouble.

255
00:14:25,900 --> 00:14:28,420
But to Jia Changchao and Xia Song,

256
00:14:28,420 --> 00:14:29,740
I’m just the same kind of person

257
00:14:30,180 --> 00:14:31,940
like you.

258
00:14:32,820 --> 00:14:34,100
I came to see you off.

259
00:14:34,260 --> 00:14:37,500
It’s just two persons in strait

260
00:14:37,500 --> 00:14:39,740
trying to get some comfort from each other.

261
00:14:40,580 --> 00:14:41,540
It should be alright.

262
00:14:42,580 --> 00:14:43,820
You came here

263
00:14:43,820 --> 00:14:45,220
not just for seeing me off, right?

264
00:14:49,340 --> 00:14:50,820
For victims along the river.

265
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:58,260
Why can’t we go to see Yanguo off?

266
00:15:03,700 --> 00:15:04,940
We have to avoid arousing suspicion

267
00:15:06,620 --> 00:15:07,660
