268
00:15:08,500 --> 00:15:10,140
That’s mere a frame-up!

269
00:15:11,340 --> 00:15:12,060
Right?

270
00:15:21,620 --> 00:15:23,460
Clique, clique…

271
00:15:24,860 --> 00:15:25,620
Alright!

272
00:15:26,420 --> 00:15:27,660
Even if we are a clique,

273
00:15:28,500 --> 00:15:29,860
we are a clique of upright people.

274
00:15:35,340 --> 00:15:36,140
Yongshu,

275
00:15:37,300 --> 00:15:39,460
no matter what kind of clique it is,

276
00:15:40,220 --> 00:15:42,060
clique itself is always a taboo.

277
00:15:50,820 --> 00:15:54,820
= Clique =

278
00:16:04,220 --> 00:16:04,860
Your Majesty,

279
00:16:05,100 --> 00:16:06,980
Physician Zhang wants to see you.

280
00:16:10,140 --> 00:16:10,860
Your...

281
00:16:22,460 --> 00:16:23,420
Your Majesty,

282
00:16:24,060 --> 00:16:25,860
