567
00:34:21,540 --> 00:34:22,580
into the escaped maid.

568
00:34:23,020 --> 00:34:24,180
Madam Zhang always has this thing in mind.

569
00:34:26,620 --> 00:34:27,380
It’s not easy

570
00:34:27,380 --> 00:34:28,860
