574
00:34:34,140 --> 00:34:35,740
Don’t pretend to be a well-behaved person.

575
00:34:36,380 --> 00:34:37,820
What you did to Fu Bi and Shi Jie

576
00:34:37,820 --> 00:34:39,100
is so smart

577
00:34:39,300 --> 00:34:40,820
that even the Imperial Security Agency
didn’t find out.

578
00:34:42,180 --> 00:34:45,540
And also, it’s you who sent someone

579
00:34:45,780 --> 00:34:47,100
to scare Shi Jie, isn’t it?

580
00:34:52,620 --> 00:34:56,100
As long as one sage comes forward,
other sages will follow up.

581
00:34:56,340 --> 00:35:00,140
Eliminating villains is like removing chicken feet
to make them unable to do bad things anymore.

582
00:35:03,620 --> 00:35:04,940
I, Xia Song

583
00:35:05,220 --> 00:35:07,180
the villain

584
00:35:07,180 --> 00:35:08,780
once demoted by His Majesty,

585
00:35:09,420 --> 00:35:10,220
am back,

586
00:35:12,580 --> 00:35:15,780
