601
00:36:04,780 --> 00:36:06,060
But something’s weird recently.

602
00:36:06,900 --> 00:36:09,140
Yang Huaimin has never come out.

603
00:36:09,980 --> 00:36:11,180
Before we agreed

604
00:36:11,380 --> 00:36:12,420
