608
00:36:17,020 --> 00:36:19,060
I’ve sent someone to wait for him twice,

609
00:36:19,300 --> 00:36:20,260
but he never showed up.

610
00:36:29,820 --> 00:36:31,820
His Majesty looks weird too.

611
00:36:35,620 --> 00:36:38,620
Wait, something must happen.

612
00:36:39,020 --> 00:36:40,860
There must be something wrong in the palace.

613
00:36:41,300 --> 00:36:42,340
When will you go back?

614
00:36:45,420 --> 00:36:46,300
I’m leaving now.

615
00:36:49,740 --> 00:36:51,260
Don’t, don’t go.

616
00:36:52,700 --> 00:36:54,540
It’s not easy for you to come out,

617
00:36:54,660 --> 00:36:55,340
