630
00:37:35,860 --> 00:37:37,740
Put it in every corner.

631
00:37:47,140 --> 00:37:47,780
Come here.

632
00:37:51,980 --> 00:37:52,620
Your Majesty,

633
00:37:53,300 --> 00:37:55,500
Manager Zhang Maoze is outside.

634
00:38:01,500 --> 00:38:02,300
Your Majesty,

635
00:38:10,180 --> 00:38:11,300
