653
00:38:46,780 --> 00:38:49,114
and physicians were sent to
all counties to distribute medicines,

654
00:38:49,120 --> 00:38:50,474
to save lives and take precautions.

655
00:38:51,060 --> 00:38:51,940
What Your Majesty did

656
00:38:52,260 --> 00:38:54,260
saved countless lives.

657
00:39:00,860 --> 00:39:01,740
Not me,

658
00:39:20,780 --> 00:39:21,900
it’s Zuixinglai.

659
00:39:28,220 --> 00:39:29,180
It’s Zuixinglai.

660
00:39:36,940 --> 00:39:37,660
Tell me,

661
00:39:38,780 --> 00:39:40,100
is it a destined task to Zuixinglai

662
00:39:40,100 --> 00:39:40,860
