663
00:39:42,340 --> 00:39:43,540
In the past, Shen Nong

664
00:39:43,940 --> 00:39:45,220
tried hundreds of herbs for his people

665
00:39:45,220 --> 00:39:46,260
to cure them.

666
00:39:47,180 --> 00:39:49,460
So, so,

667
00:39:49,860 --> 00:39:50,820
so Zuixinglai

668
00:39:51,020 --> 00:39:52,740
is the future emperor

669
00:39:52,740 --> 00:39:53,820
Heaven chose for our people.

670
00:39:54,260 --> 00:39:55,020
Right?

671
00:39:58,460 --> 00:39:59,260
Your Majesty,

672
00:40:00,180 --> 00:40:05,020
Heaven will protect the prince.

673
00:40:09,540 --> 00:40:10,340
I’ll appoint him as the successor.

674
00:40:12,020 --> 00:40:13,140
I’ll appoint Zuixinglai,

675
00:40:14,380 --> 00:40:15,580
Zhao Xin, the Second Prince

676
00:40:16,940 --> 00:40:18,140
