677
00:40:18,580 --> 00:40:19,340
Someone!

678
00:40:24,340 --> 00:40:25,100
My successor…

679
00:40:27,340 --> 00:40:28,020
Your Highness,

680
00:40:29,580 --> 00:40:30,340
Your Highness.

681
00:40:31,020 --> 00:40:32,660
Prince’s fever is gone,

682
00:40:33,060 --> 00:40:34,500
